modules.description: Converts OCaml parsetrees between versions 4.02 to 4.06, supporting bidirectional transformations between adjacent releases. Operates on OCaml's internal parsetree structures, preserving syntax and annotations during conversion. Enables migration of codebases between OCaml compiler versions without manual rewriting.

Handles the migration of parse tree data by dispatching to specific transformation hooks. Operates on OCaml build plugin hooks and parse tree structures. Used to update legacy parse tree formats during build processes.
